Find trajectories in the MST All the trajectory or choose the nodes.

find_trajectories.Rd

Find trajectories in the MST All the trajectory or choose the nodes.

find_trajectories(processed_data, f_sim_map, f_graph)

Arguments

processed_data

Dataframe. Processed from original data.
f_sim_map

TDAmapper object.
f_graph

igraph object, out put from graph.adjacency.

Value

Dataframe with different similarity measures

Examples

my_tda <- map_tda(scaled_lab_mat)
my_graph <- make_tda_graph(my_tda, sim_dat, 'time')

my_trajs <- find_trajectories(sim_dat, my_tda, my_graph)
